      "source": "ttn-example",
      "_note": "Upstream cpl01-codec.yaml example input (fPort 4); oracle TDC=3236238, DISALARM=1, KEEP_STATUS=0, KEEP_TIME=24974, TRIGGER_MODE=1 mapped to camelCase extras (booleans for 0/1 flags)."
    },
    {
      "description": "fPort 5 device status: model, firmware, battery volts",
